text: Jerry Powell (10 July 1852 - 3 September 1913) was an Australian cricketer. He played fifteen first-class matches for New South Wales between 1872/73 and 1884/85. ==See also== * List of New South Wales representative cricketers ==References== ==External links== * Category:1852 births Category:1913 deaths Category:Australian cricketers Category:New South Wales cricketers
title: Jerry Powell
